406
00:22:27,208 --> 00:22:33,083
♪ THAT'S WHEN I WILL FIND
THE LOVE I KEEP INSIDE ♪

407
00:22:33,166 --> 00:22:38,333
♪ WHEN YOU'RE WITH ME
AND YOU TAKE MY HAND ♪

408
00:22:38,416 --> 00:22:44,625
♪ SOMEHOW EVERYTHING
SEEMS TO WORK ITSELF OUT RIGHT ♪

409
00:22:44,708 --> 00:22:50,333
♪ WHEN I SEE YOUR EYES
STARING BACK AT MINE ♪

410
00:22:50,416 --> 00:22:56,500
♪ THERE INSIDE I FIND
A LOVE THAT NEVER DIES ♪

411
00:22:56,583 --> 00:23:00,833
♪ TOGETHER I KNOW
WE'LL FIND A WAY ♪

412
00:23:00,916 --> 00:23:03,583
♪ JUST YOU AND I ♪

413
00:23:17,833 --> 00:23:19,333
- Yamato: YOU'RE
DOING SELF-TRAINING TOO?

414
00:23:19,416 --> 00:23:22,208
COOL! GOOD LUCK, ASAHINA!

415
00:23:22,291 --> 00:23:24,666
- DO YOU REALLY THINK YOU HAVE
TIME TO CHEER PEOPLE UP?

416
00:23:24,750 --> 00:23:26,416
IF YOU CHANGE YOUR RUNNING STYLE
THAT QUICKLY

417
00:23:26,500 --> 00:23:27,833
YOU'RE GONNA RETURN
TO YOUR OLD HABITS

418
00:23:27,916 --> 00:23:29,541
WITHOUT EVEN REALIZING IT!

419
00:23:29,625 --> 00:23:31,708
- Yamato: I DON'T GET IT!
WHAT DID I DO TO HER?

